<p>
<lb n="1"/>© śrīmaḍ bāḷacaṁdra siddhāntadē
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vara guḍḍi perggaḍe vāsiyaṇnana pe
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇḍati cāmikabbe tribhuvanatiḷakada
<lb n="4"/>riṣisamudāyadāhāradānaṁ vṛddhi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yiṁ naḍevantāgi koṭṭa gadyāṇaṁ pa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>dinaydu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> © <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

